:"2019-07-21T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄭重呼籲：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果返緊或即將返到元朗既手足，如果肚餓或者肚痛，可以去屯門天圍大個解食個野，如果留戀龍九既，就珍惜同龍九每一份一秒<br />\n#公眾安全情報 #721大遊行 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n元朗月台有衫拎！<br />\n元朗月台有衫拎！<br />\n元朗月台有衫拎！<br />\n<br />\n🚃港鐵由屯門避過雞地返元朗攻略🚃<br />\n<br />\n兆康站<br />\n步行10分鐘至富泰邨對面巴士站坐紅Van （可達元朗廣場、教育路、總站匯豐）<br />\n步行10分鐘至富泰邨對面巴士站坐九巴53（可達大馬路沿途）<br />\n<br />\n天水圍轉輕鐵都可以返元朗<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6d0f2bbc2c1dbaca1ac9c82c008c8f2b66d4b6b9","tid":1338281,"uid":73310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"627982222b30ca325555a3382ce4144134b047f2","tid":1338281,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:50:48.000Z","msg":"不如大家買車飛 唔好留散紙<br />\n留散紙都要時間買 <br />\n同埋直接攞車飛方便好多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"好埋唔會比狗偷錢"},{"pid":"00a69ece4b590ff34f81e40e45746642358ad802","tid":1338281,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"遍地開花可以apply落派飛度：<br />\n1. 喺站內派<br />\n2. 買完拎出站派，派俾有需要嘅人攞<br />\n3. 周圍痴 （唔太prefer）<br />\n<br />\n最緊要spread risk，唔好疊埋一齊，如果唔係就俾人一次過攞晒，"},{"pid":"977112336f760dcf74b0bc71e2282b9517389589","tid":1338281,"uid":115337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"買車飛唔好留散紙"},{"pid":"232192cb20a3a95f04eb6c7d77c36987689d1ebc","tid":1338281,"uid":78998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:27:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ef3c606cf4c295c4d6cfcd32c5579c1c0e9ef6a","tid":1338281,"uid":168541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"手足見到有散紙係機上面<br />\n幫手買飛去派"},{"pid":"1e3f558